            &hml LEFT_SHIFT A  &hml LEFT_CONTROL S  &hml LALT D  &hml LEFT_COMMAND F  &kp G      &kp H      &hmr LGUI J      &hmr LALT K               &hmr LCMD L  &hmr LSHFT L
&kp LSHIFT  &kp Z              &kp X                &kp C        &kp V                &kp B      &kp N      &kp M            &hmr LA(LG(LCTRL)) COMMA  &kp DOT      &kp FSLH      &kp RSHIFT
                                                    &lt 4 ESC    &lt 3 SPACE          &kp TAB    &lt 2 RET  &lt 1 BACKSPACE  &lt 5 DEL
