        SYM {
            bindings = <
        &kp LEFT_BRACE  &kp LS(AMPS)  &kp ASTRK             &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS   &kp RIGHT_BRACE    &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans
        &kp SQT         &kp DOLLAR    &kp PERCENT           &kp CARET              &kp PLUS           &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans
&trans  &kp TILDE       &kp EXCL      &kp AT                &kp HASH               &kp PIPE           &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans
                                      &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS  &kp MINUS          &trans  &trans  &trans
            >;
